---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Refund and Cancellation Policy" description="Read the Refund and Cancellation Policy of Global Yoga Tips. Learn about eligibility and processing times.">
  <!-- Top Banner -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-secondary-bg/30 border-b border-border-main/40 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="text-xs uppercase font-bold text-brand-primary tracking-wider">Compliance</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main">Refund and Cancellation Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-base max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Effective date: June 22, 2026. Clear guidelines about refunds for our digital self-care products.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Refund Policy Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white border border-border-main rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-sm">
      <div class="prose prose-indigo max-w-none text-text-secondary text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-0 mb-4">1. Digital Products Policy</h2>
        <p>
          At Global Yoga Tips, we sell **digital wellness programs, yoga calendars, and meditation blueprints**. Because our products are digital assets that are delivered instantly upon purchase and cannot be returned, we maintain the following refund terms:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>7-Day Satisfaction Guarantee:</strong> We want you to love your self-care journey. If you are not satisfied with your purchase, you may request a full refund within <strong>7 days</strong> of your purchase date.</li>
          <li><strong>Post-7 Days:</strong> No refunds are issued for any reason after 7 days have elapsed from the purchase date.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">2. Processing of Refunds</h2>
        <p>
          Once your refund request is received and approved:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Your access to the premium yoga program and dashboard materials will be revoked immediately.</li>
          <li>The refund will be processed, and a credit will automatically be applied to your original method of payment (Credit Card, Debit Card, UPI, Net Banking, or Wallet).</li>
          <li>Please allow <strong>5 to 7 business days</strong> for the refunded amount to reflect in your bank account, depending on your bank's processing cycles.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">3. Subscription Cancellation</h2>
        <p>
          If we introduce monthly or yearly subscription-based memberships in the future:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>You can cancel your subscription at any time directly through your User Dashboard.</li>
          <li>Upon cancellation, you will retain access to the premium content until the end of your current billing cycle. No partial refunds are provided for remaining days in a billing period.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">4. Abuse of Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to refuse refunds to users who exhibit a pattern of abusing our satisfaction guarantee (e.g., repeatedly purchasing programs and requesting refunds shortly thereafter).
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">5. Contact Support</h2>
        <p>
          To initiate a refund request or ask questions about our cancellation policy, please reach out to us at:
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium text-text-main">
          Email: <a href="mailto:refunds@globalyogatips.com" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">refunds@globalyogatips.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
